{"content": "I need to multiply 81a \u00d7 797 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 81a (base 11) to base 10**\n- 81a\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 10\u00d711\u2070\n- = 8\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 10\u00d71\n- = 968 + 11 + 10\n- = 989\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 797 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 797\u2081\u2081 = 7\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n- = 7\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 7\u00d71\n- = 847 + 99 + 7\n- = 953\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 989 \u00d7 953 = 942,517\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 942,517 back to base 11**\n- 942,517 \u00f7 11 = 85,683 R 4\n- 85,683 \u00f7 11 = 7,789 R 4\n- 7,789 \u00f7 11 = 708 R 1\n- 708 \u00f7 11 = 64 R 4\n- 64 \u00f7 11 = 5 R 9\n- 5 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 5\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 594144\n\n594144", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 392}